@page "/"

<PageTitle>Can I Do Your Dishes? - Why I Want to Help Young Families</PageTitle>

<div class="content-section">
    <section class="reason-card">
        <h2>Family Time Matters</h2>
        <p>
            Young families are juggling so much - careers, children, household responsibilities, and trying to find moments of connection. 
            The last thing you need to worry about is a sink full of dishes at the end of a long day.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="reason-card">
        <h2>Small Acts, Big Impact</h2>
        <p>
            By taking care of your dishes and chores, I'm giving you back precious time - time to read bedtime stories, 
            time to relax together, time to just be present with your family without the weight of household tasks.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="reason-card">
        <h2>Community Support</h2>
        <p>
            I believe in supporting families in my community. When families thrive, our whole community benefits. 
            This is my way of contributing to that strength and well-being.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="reason-card">
        <h2>Simple, Reliable Service</h2>
        <p>
            No complicated contracts, no hidden fees. Just honest, reliable help when you need it most. 
            Because everyone deserves a break, and everyone deserves a clean kitchen.
        </p>
    </section>
</div>

